&lt;p&gt;Join us! The &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.classy.org/&quot;&gt;GoFundMe Pro&lt;/a&gt; team is seeking a dynamic and high-performing Enterprise Account Executive with a proven track record in selling technology products and/or services to large commercial, public sector, and/or nonprofit organizations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
